(secondQuint)Pilot Study of Skin Quality Improvement After Adipose-drived Stem Cell Transfer in Irradiated Breasts.

 10 participants who taken conservative mastectomy will be enrolled 1.

 Process - adipose tissue is obtained from the subject's thigh or abdomen - adipose-drived stromal vascular fraction(SVF)cell isolation using automatic centrifuge system - adipose-drived stromal vascular fraction(SVF)cell graft into the irradiated breast.

 2.

 Duration of study - entire duration: approximate 30weeks - Follow-up period: 12 weeks - Enrollment period: 12 weeks 3.

